<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-researchers-link-car-t-cell-aging-to-cancer-relapse/">Mayo Clinic researchers link CAR-T cell aging to cancer relapse&nbsp;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
