					<description><![CDATA[<p>A Mayo discovery could lead to future strategies for detecting the disease in its earliest, precancerous stages.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-researchers-capture-first-signs-of-ovarian-cancer-risk/">Mayo Clinic researchers capture first signs of ovarian cancer risk</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
